    • Customer

      public Customer(int customerId, String username, String password, String email, String phoneNumber, String branch, String accountType, String credit_card, String address, String work_address, int has_discount_code, int userID)
      Constructs a Customer object with specified values.
      Parameters:
      customerId - the customer ID
      username - the username
      password - the password
      email - the email address
      phoneNumber - the phone number
      branch - the branch associated with the customer
      accountType - the type of account
      credit_card - the credit card information
      address - the residential address
      work_address - the work address
      has_discount_code - indicates if the customer has a discount code (1 for yes, 0 for no)
      userID - the user ID associated with the customer
